<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width" name="viewport">
    <title>Add claim: Permanent Impairment | MyService</title>
    <link href="docs/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid uikit-refactor">
    <noscript>
        <p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p>
    </noscript>
    <nav class="uikit-skip-link">
        <a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a>
    </nav>
    <% include ../../../global/partials/header-topbar.ejs %>
        <% include ../../../global/partials/header-claims.ejs %>
            <% include ../partials/help-button.ejs %>
                <main>
                    <div class="section-feature border-bottom--mild margin-above--none margin-below--none padding-below">
                        <div class="container margin-above--none">
                            <h1 class="margin-above--none">
                                <span class="heading">Getting started</span>
                            </h1>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="container" id="main-content">

                        <p class="margin-above--large margin-below--large">When determining your level of
                            <i>Permanent Impairment</i> compensation, we look at the affect your conditions have on your lifestyle.
                            The
                            <i>Lifestyle Questionnaire</i> is your opportunity to contribute to this decision.</p>

                        <div class="form-group pt-flow--student pt-flow--claimant">

                            <legend class="legend-label margin-below">Select an option to get started</legend>
                            <div class="radio-tile--group radio-tile--medium">
                                <label class="radio-tile">
                                    <input id="lsq-pathway-tellstory" class="sr" type="radio" name="confirmStudentOrClaimant" value="student">
                                    <span>
                                        <img src="../../../../docs/images/ico-message.svg"> I want to tell DVA how my conditions affect my lifestyle
                                    </span>
                                </label>

                                <label class="radio-tile">
                                    <input id="lsq-pathway-dvadoit" class="sr" type="radio" name="confirmStudentOrClaimant" value="guardian">
                                    <span>
                                        <img src="../../../../docs/images/ico-folder.svg"> I want DVA to make a decision based on my medical reports
                                    </span>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info margin-below--large" style="display:none;" id="lsq-pathway-tellstory--info">
                            <p>When completing this questionnaire, take into consideration your accepted conditions. Refer to
                                your 'Permanent Impairment Lifestyle Questionnaire' email to see what conditions are included.
                            </p>
                        </div>


                        <div class="pagination">
                            <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/index-claims'">Back to Claims page</button>
                            <div class="floated">
                                <button class="uikit-btn btnNext" id="btnNext" onclick="window.location.href = '/pi-claim1'">Save and next</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <% include ../partials/cancel-modal.ejs %>
                    </div>

                </main>

                <% include ../../../global/partials/footer.ejs %>
                    <% include ../partials/panel-help.ejs %>

                        <script>

                            // Dynamic content for LSQ pathway
                            $("#lsq-pathway-tellstory").click(function () {
                                $("#lsq-pathway-tellstory--info").show();
                            });
                            $("#lsq-pathway-dvadoit").click(function () {
                                $("#lsq-pathway-tellstory--info").hide();
                            });
                        </script>

</body>

</html>